1.name: Aura_svireposti
1.title: Aura of Ferocity
1.body:
!element !lvl !cost !radius !energy !time !cooldawn !preparation !dDecreases your armor by 30%. Your weapon attacks increase physical damage done by your party members by !e1% for 10 seconds.
Cast this spell again to remove this effect.
*You cannot use this spell when your shield is equipped.*

2.name: Bezjalostnost
2.title: Ruthlessness
2.body: !lvl !cost !dEach "Agonizing Strike" to the target affected by the "Jagged Slice" effect extends the duration of that effect by !e1 second.

0.body: Extends the duration of "Jagged Slice" by !e1 seconds

3.name: Bezuprechnaya_ataka
3.title: Flawless Strike
3.body:
!element !lvl !cost !range !energy !time !cooldawn !preparation !dInflicts <:!e1:> to <:!e2:> damage and has a 20% chance to cause the target to bleed for !timeTT(10+!Glubokoe_rassechenie.e1), receiving <:!damage:> periodic damage.
If enemies are knocked down, 50% more damage is inflicted (<:!e1*1.5:>-<:!e2*1.5:>) and the chance of causing the target to bleed is doubled (<:!e3*2:>%).
"Generates 20 combat advantage."
!do

2.body: Chance to apply bleed effect increased by !e1%.

3.body: Duration of the bleed effect increased by !timeTT(!e1)

0.body: Can be used after a successful hit

2.body: Stun duration decreased by 50%.

10.name: Veernaya_ataka
10.title: Cleave
10.body:
!element !lvl !cost !range !energy !time !cooldawn !preparation !dInflicts <:!e1:>-<:!e2:> damage to all enemies in front of you.
Has a <:!e3:>% chance to cause the target to bleed.
Bleeding enemies will take 50% more damage.
Has a !e4% chance to grant the Rampage effect which increases your damage dealt by 5% and reduces your armor by 5% for each stack of the Rampage effect.
Effect can stack up to 5 times.
Using Cleave against bleeding enemies will increase your chance to gain the Rampage effect by !e5%.

691.name: Bogatirskaya_sila
691.title: Heroic Might
691.body:
!lvl !element !cost !range !mana !time !cooldown !preparation !dGenerates 3 stacks of the "Heroic Might" effect for 20 seconds. Each time you use the "Forceful Kick", "Punch", "Hack", "Devastating Blow" and "Flawless Strike" 1 stack of the effect is consumed. Your abilities additionally inflict <:!e1*(1.1+0.1*$t):> damage. "Forceful Kick" and "Punch" effects knock the target back 20m. "Hack" effect immobilizes the target for <:2.4+0.4*$t:>s. "Devastating Blow" and "Flawless Strike" cause "Deep Wound" effect inflicting additional <:!e2:> damage each second for 3 seconds.

*Consumes 3 Tears of Dragon.*
Using Tears of Dragon of a higher quality increases additional damage dealt by the "Heroic Might" effect and duration of the "Broken Legs" effect.
